0.1.name: wordpress/funny-demotivators
0.1.description: Demotivational Post widget add to your website new page with big collection of Demotivational Posters . All pictures hosting in http://demotivationalpost.com so you don't pay for transfer. If user click some picture he open new tab with source of picture. All pictures are checked by moderator and will be grabbed from home page http://demotivationalpost.com , you can see how working this widget in my sample blog http://funmot.com/english/Demotivational-posters/ If plugin not work try to disable recent posts or use another theme.
